statements: SELECT name FROM contacts WHERE ANY child.age > 14 AND child.gender = "m" OVER child IN children END
SELECT name FROM contacts WHERE ANY child.age > 14 OVER child IN children END
SELECT name FROM contacts WHERE ANY child.age > 14 OVER child IN children END AND ANY hobby = "golf" OVER hobby IN hobbies END
SELECT title FROM catalog WHERE ANY director OVER director IN details.director END
SELECT details.director FROM catalog  GROUP BY details.director HAVING ANY director OVER director IN details.director END
SELECT asin FROM catalog WHERE dimensions.height > 1 and ANY gen = "Thriller" OVER gen IN details.genre END

SELECT search_history FROM user_profile WHERE (ANY (search.category = "Films" AND ANY subcat = "Comedy" OVER subcat IN search.sub-category END) OVER search IN search_history END) AND (ANY (search.category = "Books" AND ANY subcat LIKE "History%" OVER subcat IN search.sub-category END) OVER search IN search_history END) AND (ANY (search.category = "Music" AND ANY subcat LIKE "%Folk" OVER subcat IN search.sub-category END) OVER search IN search_history END)
SELECT id FROM orders WHERE ALL product LIKE "tea_11" OVER product IN ARRAY ol.productId OVER ol IN orderlines END END
SELECT id FROM orders WHERE ANY product LIKE "______" OVER product IN ARRAY ol.productId OVER ol IN orderlines END END
SELECT id FROM orders WHERE ALL product NOT LIKE "tea11%" OVER product IN ARRAY ol.productId OVER ol IN orderlines END END
SELECT id FROM orders WHERE ANY product NOT LIKE "tea11%" OVER product IN ARRAY ol.productId OVER ol IN orderlines END END
